N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 169.9 - Judicial review

State Regulations

In the letter transmitting the decision, the hearing officer
shall make clear references to the availability of judicial review, pursuant to
article 78 of the Civil Practice Law and Rules. Notes
